Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪里?他躲在哪里?\N{\rEng}Where is he? Where is he hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道,我从昨天就一直在找他\N{\rEng}I don't know. I've been looking for him since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我再问你最后一次,他在哪里?\N{\rEng}I'm gonna ask you for the last time. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要对他做什么?\N{\rEng}What are you gonna do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你留下,以免那个叛徒现身\N{\rEng}You stay here in case that rat shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在保护谁?愚蠢的混账\N{\rEng}Who you protecting, you dumb asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一个出卖朋友的下三滥?\N{\rEng}A stoolie who rats on his own friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也曾经是你的朋友\N{\rEng}They were your friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了,你想跟那个贱人落得一个下场是吧?\N{\rEng}I got it. You wanna end up like that bitch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在陈罗的中国戏院\N{\rEng}At Chun Lao's. Chinese theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你留下看着这个混帐东西\N{\rEng}You stay here with this barrel of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,面条…\N{\rEng}Noodles. Noodles. Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,放松…\N{\rEng}Easy, easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,(禁酒令)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,(哈洛伦警长)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走,快\N{\rEng}This way. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着莫特街走,快,快,快\N{\rEng}There down. Mott Street. Go. Go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我松绑\N{\rEng}Untie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先躺下来,别动,躺着,我要他们知道是我干的\N{\rEng}Stay that way. No, stay. I want them to know I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪里?　- 去接伊芙\N{\rEng}- Where you going? - I'm gonna go get Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rEng}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经去过那里了\N{\rEng}They... They already been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么吗?\N{\rEng}Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,钱?\N{\rEng}Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的钱多得花不完　- 对,现在全都是你的了\N{\rEng}I got more than I need. - Yeah, it's all yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里?\N{\rEng}Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,先生,你要去哪里?\N{\rEng}Sir, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,随便…最近的一班巴士\N{\rEng}Anywhere. First bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,水牛城?\N{\rEng}Buffalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,单程车票\N{\rEng}One way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一块二十分\N{\rEng}That'll be $1.20.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要租一辆车\N{\rEng}I wanna rent a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请你先填这张表格好吗?\N{\rEng}Would you fill this out, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.93,0:25:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快丢骰子,兄弟,丢骰子…\N{\rEng}Shoot the dice, man. Shoot the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.47,0:29:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.35,0:29:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来归还你钟上的钥匙\N{\rEng}I brought back the key to your clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.50,0:29:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把门锁上\N{\rEng}Lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.21,0:29:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候回来的?\N{\rEng}When did you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.09,0:29:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今天　- 为什么?\N{\rEng}- Today. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们联系我　- 谁?\N{\rEng}- They got in touch with me. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.61,0:29:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你知道\N{\rEng}I thought you might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.90,0:30:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我?\N{\rEng}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.66,0:30:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在对任何人任何事都一无所知了\N{\rEng}I don't know nothing about nobody no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不请我喝一杯吗?\N{\rEng}You gonna offer me a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.17,0:30:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然…原谅我,当然,没问题\N{\rEng}Yeah, forgive me. Sure. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.09,0:30:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\rEng}Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯·威廉斯是谁?\N{\rEng}Who's Robert Williams?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我\N{\rEng}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.88,0:31:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"现告知您以下事宜：在贝希犹太墓园已被征用…"\N{\rEng}"We wish to inform you that following the sale of the Beth Israel Cemetery".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.35,0:31:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对,犹太教会堂寄出这些信,通知你将已故的亲友转葬\N{\rEng}The synagogue sent these out if you wanted to relocate your loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也收到了同样的信件,因为先父也葬在那里\N{\rEng}I got the same letter on account of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.61,0:31:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不是犹太教会堂寄的,我是上周收到的\N{\rEng}Only the synagogue didn't send that. I got that last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.25,0:31:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拉比告诉我,这些信是他八个月前寄出的\N{\rEng}The rabbi told me he sent those out about eight months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.21,0:31:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错,我就是那时候收到的\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's right. That's about when I got mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.10,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他还跟拉比说了什么?\N{\rEng}So, what else did he say to the rabbi?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.31,0:31:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他说我的运气好,菲利普·史坦\N{\rEng}He said I was lucky. The bodies of Philip Stein,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.11,0:31:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克·希密,连布可·维克兹,派崔克·高德堡的遗体已迁葬别处\N{\rEng}Maximilian Bercovicz, Patrick Goldberg were already spoken for.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在河谷区的一座豪华墓园里\N{\rEng}And they were up in a very fancy cemetery in Riverdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.68,0:32:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这代表什么意思?\N{\rEng}What's this all mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.06,0:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在说…\N{\rEng}It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.98,0:32:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"面条,不论你躲在这个狗屁世界的哪个角落,我们还是找到你了"\N{\rEng}"Hey Noodles, even though you've been hiding out in the asshole of the world, we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.20,0:32:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们知道你身在何处"\N{\rEng}We know where you are."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.83,0:32:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在说…\N{\rEng}It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"做好准备"\N{\rEng}"Get ready."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.51,0:32:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,准备什么?\N{\rEng}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.23,0:32:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,信上没写\N{\rEng}That's the one thing it didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.94,0:32:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为呢?\N{\rEng}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.15,0:33:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为答案就在这里,所以我回来了\N{\rEng}I think the answer's here. That's why I came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.32,0:33:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我把这里的东西都搬走了\N{\rEng}I moved everything in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.51,0:33:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得卖掉房子和密室\N{\rEng}I had to sell the house, the backroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.47,0:33:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以为是你拿走了那一百万\N{\rEng}You know I always thought you might have helped yourself to that million bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.53,0:33:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我知道了\N{\rEng}But now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.82,0:33:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\rEng}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.16,0:33:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你比从前还落魄\N{\rEng}You're on your ass worse than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.42,0:33:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我以为是你…\N{\rEng}But I thought it was you who...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.89,0:33:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不,你想错了\N{\rEng}No, you thought wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.35,0:33:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个行李箱空空如也\N{\rEng}The suitcase was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.28,0:34:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不然是谁拿走了?\N{\rEng}Then who took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.92,0:34:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,过去三十五年来,我一直在问自己这个问题\N{\rEng}That's what I've been asking myself for 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.41,0:34:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想看到那照片的话,我可以睡在这里\N{\rEng}If it bothers you, I can sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.50,0:34:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去睡我的房间　- 不,没关系\N{\rEng}- You can have my room. - No. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.46,0:34:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你妹妹还好吗?　- 我有好多年没见过她了\N{\rEng}- How's your sister? - I ain't seen her for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.89,0:34:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在是大明星\N{\rEng}She's a big star now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.48,0:35:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早该料到,对吧?\N{\rEng}We should have known, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.82,0:35:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你总能一开始就能看出谁是赢家\N{\rEng}You can always tell the winners at the starting gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.03,0:35:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是赢家,谁是输家,你总能一眼看出\N{\rEng}You can always tell the winners, and you can tell the losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.58,0:35:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会把钱押在你身上?\N{\rEng}Who would've put a penny on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我会孤注一掷全押你\N{\rEng}I'd have put everything I ever had on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.94,0:35:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对,然后你就会输得很惨\N{\rEng}Yeah, and you would've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.26,0:35:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你累坏了,晚安\N{\rEng}Well, you're beat. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.77,0:35:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安,摩,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Good night, Moe. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.87,0:35:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这些年来你都在做些什么?\N{\rEng}What have you been doing all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.76,0:35:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很早睡\N{\rEng}Been going to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.58,0:40:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,黛博拉,爸说你应该去帮忙\N{\rEng}Deborah, Papa says you should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.59,0:40:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不去\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.26,0:40:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,店里有一大堆客人,我们忙不过来\N{\rEng}We got customers all over. We can't do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.64,0:41:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就努力一点,我得上辩论课\N{\rEng}Try. I've got my elocution lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.20,0:41:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,肥仔,你最好去打扫下厕所,我在里面看见一只蟑螂\N{\rEng}Fat, you better spray the toilet. I saw a cockroach in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.16,0:42:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉　- 你疯啦?\N{\rEng}- Sorry. - Meshuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.39,0:42:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉,我今天没办法,明天吧\N{\rEng}Sorry, I can't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好,再见　- 再见\N{\rEng}- Okay. Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.87,0:42:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉,肥仔\N{\rEng}Sorry, Fats.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.06,0:42:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条　- 霸哥给我们了一份工作\N{\rEng}- Noodles! - Bugsy's got a job for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.56,0:42:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快点,他不等人的\N{\rEng}Hurry up. He don't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.34,0:43:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谁是蟑螂?\N{\rEng}Who you calling a cockroach?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.47,0:43:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你是什么?你如此肮脏,让我作呕\N{\rEng}So, what are you? You're filthy, you make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.81,0:43:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,像只蟑螂一样在爬厕所墙上,你说你是什么?\N{\rEng}You crawl up toilet walls just like a roach. So, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.15,0:43:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放手\N{\rEng}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.87,0:43:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你恶心是吗?那你为何秀屁股给我看?\N{\rEng}I make you sick, huh? Then how come you showed me your tush?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.96,0:43:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我给蟑螂看的\N{\rEng}To a roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.67,0:43:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你去照照镜子吧,大卫亚诺森\N{\rEng}Go look at yourself, David Aaronson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.12,0:44:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,若她继续烦我,我就给她好看\N{\rEng}She don't leave me alone, I'm gonna give her what she's asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.26,0:44:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 霸哥要怎样?　- 我们得去教训一个无赖\N{\rEng}- What's Bugsy want? - We gotta wake up a deadbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.97,0:44:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,书报摊的那个混帐不肯交钱\N{\rEng}That schmuck at the newsstand didn't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.33,0:45:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,钱给你,先生\N{\rEng}Here's your money, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.59,0:45:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\N{\rEng}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.72,0:45:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们瞧瞧,太棒了\N{\rEng}Look at it, it looks great! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧,各位\N{\rEng}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.93,0:45:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.10,0:45:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在快点做决定\N{\rEng}Now make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.73,0:46:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条,咱们拿这一块钱　- 对啊\N{\rEng}- Noodles, let's take the dollar. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.37,0:46:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了,去吧\N{\rEng}Skip, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.96,0:46:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人\N{\rEng}That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.51,0:46:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他\N{\rEng}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.01,0:46:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆,我们下周四见\N{\rEng}Hey, Sam, I'll see you next Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.97,0:46:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个人\N{\rEng}That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.94,0:46:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗?\N{\rEng}Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.15,0:46:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,霸哥说我们可以选择拿钱,或者打劫一个醉鬼\N{\rEng}Bugsy said we could take the dollar or we could roll the drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.54,0:46:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,可他还没喝醉\N{\rEng}Yeah, but he ain't even drunk yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.54,0:46:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以等\N{\rEng}We'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.05,0:46:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以去抢那个人　- 有什么好抢的?他的钱都已经买酒了\N{\rEng}- Well, you roll that one over there. - What's to roll? He drunk it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.68,0:46:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去找那个窝囊废吧\N{\rEng}Bounce that little shikker.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.81,0:47:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,外套\N{\rEng}Jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.46,0:47:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刀疤来了\N{\rEng}It's Fartface.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.06,0:47:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.23,0:47:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早该拿钱走人\N{\rEng}We should've took the dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.32,0:47:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以买十个罂粟籽腌牛肉三明治呢\N{\rEng}Could've had 10 corned beef sandwiches on poppy-seed rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.22,0:48:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,听着,用那辆马车当掩护,准备好\N{\rEng}Look, the wagon will hide us from Fartface. Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.97,0:48:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在用外套罩住他\N{\rEng}Now! Throw your jacket over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.31,0:48:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,先生你生病了吗?真可怜,你会好起来的,我来帮你\N{\rEng}Hey mister, you sick? Poor guy, you'll be okay. Come on, I'll help ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.32,0:48:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧,上车\N{\rEng}Come on, up you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.32,0:48:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我的奈森叔叔还糟糕\N{\rEng}Now, you're worse than my Uncle Nathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.16,0:49:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何要喝醉?我来带你回家吧\N{\rEng}Why do you want to get soused? You can't even walk. I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.80,0:49:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧,老妈\N{\rEng}Go, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.50,0:49:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,给我站住…嘿!说你呢\N{\rEng}Stop right there. Hey, you! Yeah, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群孩子在这里做什么?\N{\rEng}What the hell are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.52,0:49:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们这群孩子在这里做什么?　- 我们正被人欺负\N{\rEng}- What are we kids doing here? - We're getting it up the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.82,0:49:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对,我们正被人耍,这也违法吗?\N{\rEng}Yeah, getting screwed. Is there a law against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.28,0:49:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能请你施舍一毛钱,以免我们被人欺负吗?\N{\rEng}Can you spare a dime for pisherkehs that just got it up the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.41,0:49:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快点滚,滚出这条街\N{\rEng}Get out of here. Get off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.34,0:49:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开,离开这条街\N{\rEng}Get out of here. Get off the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.92,0:49:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快点滚,别再回来\N{\rEng}Go ahead. And don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.30,0:49:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再在这里看到你们,明白吗?\N{\rEng}I don't want to see you here again. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.50,0:50:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚点再去你家找你\N{\rEng}Hey, stop by for you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.89,0:50:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好,直接来这厕所找我就行\N{\rEng}Yeah, but knock here on the john first.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.11,0:50:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我老爸在祷告,我老妈在哭泣,灯都熄了\N{\rEng}My old man's praying, and my old lady's crying. And the light's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.50,0:50:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我还回家做什么?在这里我至少还能看看书\N{\rEng}What the hell should I go home for? At least in here I can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.73,0:51:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要去哪里?　- 妈,别生气\N{\rEng}- Where do you think you're going? - Mama, don't get worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.15,0:51:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先把锅洗了\N{\rEng}You got pots to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.92,0:51:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,佩姬?\N{\rEng}Peggeleh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.71,0:51:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来,妈,我要先上个厕所\N{\rEng}I'll be right back, Ma. I gotta go to the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.19,0:52:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,佩姬\N{\rEng}Hi, Peggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.82,0:52:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你该把门锁上\N{\rEng}At least you could lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.79,0:52:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢吗?\N{\rEng}Don't you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.97,0:52:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过更大的\N{\rEng}I've seen better.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.98,0:52:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你见识过很多吗?　- 你又见识过多少?\N{\rEng}- You seen lots? - How many you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.98,0:52:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你我见识过多少,一个都没有\N{\rEng}I'll tell you how many. None.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.46,0:52:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看你那里\N{\rEng}Let me see yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.57,0:52:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只能看不能摸\N{\rEng}Looksies, no feelsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.08,0:52:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,佩姬,我…\N{\rEng}Peggy... Peggy, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.60,0:52:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…\N{\rEng}I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.27,0:53:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢这样对吗?　- 我不喜欢免费服务\N{\rEng}- You like it, don't you? - Not for free, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.56,0:53:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给我买个奶油蛋糕,然后想对我怎样都行\N{\rEng}You bring me a charlotte russe with whipped cream, and then you can do anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.99,0:53:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明天,我明天就带来给你\N{\rEng}Tomorrow. I'll bring it to you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.91,0:53:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明天我就带来　- 我这里概不赊账\N{\rEng}- I'll bring it to you tomorrow. - Look, I don't give credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.08,0:53:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证,我保证\N{\rEng}I promise. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.80,0:53:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好停手,快把屎拉在裤子上了\N{\rEng}You better stop squeezing me, or I'm gonna poop in my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.44,0:53:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不出去吗?\N{\rEng}Well, you getting out?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.22,0:54:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,给我,快点…\N{\rEng}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.94,0:54:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来六张\N{\rEng}Give me six copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.66,0:54:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你把裤子脱了,我就再让你爽一次\N{\rEng}Drop your pants and I'll stick it to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.88,0:54:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么叫做再?　- 这可说来话长\N{\rEng}- What do you mean, "again"? - That's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.39,0:55:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,先来瞧瞧现在几点了\N{\rEng}And look what time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.61,0:55:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已经六点三十四分,我得走啦\N{\rEng}It's already 6:34. And I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.20,0:55:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊,一堆事情等着我呢\N{\rEng}Boy, I got a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.54,0:55:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}Hold it a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.67,0:55:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经是六点三十五分,我可闲得很\N{\rEng}Now it's 6:35. And I ain't got a damn thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.72,0:55:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你等着瞧,混蛋,我会让你吃不完兜着走\N{\rEng}Just you wait, asshole. I'll do something with your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.73,0:55:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,慢着,嘿\N{\rEng}Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.23,0:55:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们说起时间\N{\rEng}Since we're talking about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.69,0:55:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎你会在六点三十六分时,摔碎那盏灯\N{\rEng}...it looks like you're gonna break that lamp at 6:36.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.83,0:55:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是从哪偷来的?　- 这是我的\N{\rEng}- Where'd you pinch this? - It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.54,0:55:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能证明吗?　- 是我给他的\N{\rEng}- Prove it. - I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.01,0:55:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.47,0:55:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈是谁?\N{\rEng}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.93,0:55:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你从哪里来?　- 布朗克斯\N{\rEng}- Where you from? - The Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.19,0:55:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你随便就把怀表送人?\N{\rEng}And you give away watches?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我叔叔\N{\rEng}He's my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.53,0:55:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那这是谁给你的?　- 我的奈森叔叔\N{\rEng}- And who gave it to you? - My Uncle Nathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.83,0:55:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟\N{\rEng}My little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.17,0:55:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你叔叔来警局一趟\N{\rEng}Tell your uncle to stop by the precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.46,0:56:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他死了　- 酗酒\N{\rEng}- He's dead. - Alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.51,0:56:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,死在波兰的基希纳乌\N{\rEng}In Kishnev, Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.52,0:56:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那他再也用不着它了,现在它被充公了\N{\rEng}Then he don't need it no more. It's been requisitioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.82,0:56:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么意思?　- 在六点三十七分,怀表被他抢走了\N{\rEng}- What's that mean? - Pinched, by him. At 6:37.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.71,0:56:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,记住,我盯上你们俩了\N{\rEng}Just remember, I got my eye on you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.05,0:56:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也盯上你了\N{\rEng}I got my eye on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.47,0:56:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我一把,快,把灯拿起来,我撑不住了\N{\rEng}Take it! Take it! Take the lamp off. I can't hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.40,0:56:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.04,0:56:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\rEng}Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.79,0:56:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我叔叔\N{\rEng}My uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.47,0:57:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个,有鲜奶油的那个　- 五分钱的那个?\N{\rEng}- That one. With the cream. - The 5-cent one?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.56,0:57:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.19,0:57:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,买两分钱的蛋糕她只会帮我打手枪,这我自己来就行\N{\rEng}For the two penny one she only gives you a hand job. I can do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.06,0:57:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个\N{\rEng}Not that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.69,0:57:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是那一个\N{\rEng}That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.28,0:57:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,确定?\N{\rEng}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.74,0:57:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,包得漂亮一点\N{\rEng}Wrap it up pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.45,0:58:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,早安,佩姬在家吗?\N{\rEng}Good morning. Peggy home?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.46,0:58:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她在洗澡\N{\rEng}She's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.59,0:58:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了,麻烦你跟她说一声我来了\N{\rEng}That's great. Would you be so kind that... Tell her I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.34,0:58:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈,再给我一桶水\N{\rEng}Hey, Ma. Another bucket of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.10,0:58:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.48,1:00:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想怎样?　- 我吗?\N{\rEng}- What do you want? - Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.86,1:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈妈说你找我　- 不,那些人和我说…\N{\rEng}- Mama said you were looking for me. - No. The guys told me that...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.04,1:00:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么?　- 我改天再来吧\N{\rEng}- What? - I'll come back some other time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.24,1:01:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.34,1:01:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,面条…\N{\rEng}Noodles! Noodles! Noodles!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.75,1:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你拍到了吗?\N{\rEng}Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.34,1:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他的屁股动个不停,但我拍到了\N{\rEng}His big ass so blinked, but we got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.80,1:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的,刀疤,还是上班时间\N{\rEng}Nice going, Fartface. And on duty too.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.20,1:01:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们拍到了我没穿裤子的照片?\N{\rEng}You boys caught me with my pants down that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.10,1:01:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不,我们拍到你在和未成年少女乱搞\N{\rEng}No, we caught you with your schmuck in a minor.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.35,1:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快把这放在安全的地方　- 算我倒霉,嘿,等一下\N{\rEng}- Scram, put this someplace safe. - That's all right. Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.35,1:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪里?站住,等一下\N{\rEng}Where you going? Stop! Hold! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.82,1:02:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,你,站住\N{\rEng}Hey, you, stop! Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.78,1:02:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们要怎么处理照片?　- 这得看情况,现在几点?麦克希\N{\rEng}- What are you kids gonna do with that plate? -Depends. What time is it, Max?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.91,1:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…是时候把表拿回来了\N{\rEng}I think it's time we got our watch back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.78,1:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧,两位,咱们扯平了　- 才怪\N{\rEng}- Okay, boys, we're even. - The hell we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.00,1:02:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不会轻易放过你\N{\rEng}You'll be collecting your pension before we're even.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.58,1:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好\N{\rEng}Hiya, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.25,1:02:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想怎样?\N{\rEng}What do you boys want?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.09,1:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,首先…\N{\rEng}First off...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.64,1:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们跟佩姬做,你付钱\N{\rEng}...you're paying Peggy for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.93,1:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好,就这样?\N{\rEng}Okay. That's it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.44,1:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你先去吧,我再跟他说\N{\rEng}Go ahead while I tell him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.76,1:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信,我的第一次是个烂条子替我付钱\N{\rEng}I can't believe it. My first time, and a lousy cop's paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.48,1:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听着,你们为何还要留着那底片?\N{\rEng}Now look, what else do you kids want for that plate?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.87,1:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,面条跟我说,有一个叫做霸哥的人\N{\rEng}Noodles was telling me about a guy called Bugsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.08,1:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他能成这里的老大全靠你撑腰\N{\rEng}Seems he's boss in this neighborhood, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.09,1:02:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思?　- 意思是他买通了你\N{\rEng}- Meaning what? - Meaning he pays you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.38,1:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你能慢一点吗?不要急,慢慢来\N{\rEng}Will you slow down? What is your hurry? Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.31,1:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话你会射得很快\N{\rEng}If you keep this up, you're gonna come too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.82,1:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没?我简直不敢相信,你真是笨死了\N{\rEng}Do you see what I mean? You're so stupid. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.37,1:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以霸哥为何付钱给你?你替他做什么事?\N{\rEng}So why does Bugsy pay you? What do you do for him?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.92,1:03:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 睁一只眼闭一只眼　- 现在你对我们也得闭只眼\N{\rEng}- I close an eye once in a while. - Well, now you close an eye for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.27,1:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?你们这些人想怎样?\N{\rEng}Why? What are you kids up to?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.36,1:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他会告诉你\N{\rEng}He'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.99,1:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我,他,斜眼还有派希,我们是一伙的\N{\rEng}Me, him, Cockeye and Patsy, we're working together.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.96,1:03:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,霸哥会痛扁你们\N{\rEng}Bugsy'll flatten you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.46,1:03:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况我不能容忍别人在我的地盘上撒野\N{\rEng}Besides, I don't put up with no trouble on my beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.97,1:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你会的,而且你会闭嘴,你什么也没听见,什么也没看见\N{\rEng}You'll put up, and you'll shut up. You hear nothing, and you see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.27,1:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像你对待霸哥一样\N{\rEng}Just like you did for Bugsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.32,1:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.94,1:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别气馁,那样情况会更糟,第一次嘛,难免会这样\N{\rEng}Don't get upset. That makes it worse. It can happen the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.13,1:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都怪那两个人在那里说话　- 瞧,气氛全被你毁了\N{\rEng}- It's them two talking out there. - Can't you see you're ruining the mood?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.63,1:03:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就说定了\N{\rEng}We made our deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.72,1:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你滚吧　- 这里,亲爱的\N{\rEng}- So take a walk. - Come here, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.44,1:04:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样舒服吗?小子　- 他永远也硬不起来\N{\rEng}- Feel good, bubeleh? - He'll never get it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.58,1:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,放松,好,淡定,淡定\N{\rEng}Relax. Okay. Calm down, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.55,1:04:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好了…过来\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.95,1:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子气色好多了\N{\rEng}I'm glad the baby's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.08,1:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 逾越节快乐,黛博拉　- 逾越节快乐,贝琪\N{\rEng}- Happy Pesach, Deborah. - Happy Pesach, Becky.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.43,1:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快点,我们要迟到了\N{\rEng}Hurry. We're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.06,1:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 黛博拉在那边　- 抱歉我迟到了,妈妈需要帮忙\N{\rEng}- Oh, there's Deborah. - Sorry I'm late. Mama needed help.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.07,1:06:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,乖女孩,我刚锁门,钥匙给你\N{\rEng}Good girl. I just locked up, and I'm giving you the keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.86,1:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只要练习舞步,好吗?\N{\rEng}I thought I'd just practice my dance routines. That's all. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.16,1:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,记得别让异教徒进来\N{\rEng}Deborah, make sure you don't let the goyim in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.37,1:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好,再见　- 一会儿见,黛博拉\N{\rEng}- Okay, bye. - See you later, Debbie. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.57,1:07:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我下来,蟑螂\N{\rEng}Get down off of there, roach.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.16,1:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那张唱片就像泻药\N{\rEng}That record's just like Ex-Lax.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.08,1:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我一播放你就进厕所\N{\rEng}Every time I put it on, you have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.33,1:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.13,1:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我来一杯酒　- 我们今天不营业\N{\rEng}- Give me a drink. - We're closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.13,1:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好人不会在逾越节喝酒,他们都去集会了\N{\rEng}Nice people don't drink on Pesach. They go to the synagogue.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.85,1:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那你在这里做什么?\N{\rEng}So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.02,1:08:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,某人得看着这个地方\N{\rEng}Somebody's got to keep an eye on the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.90,1:08:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,外面小偷很多,稍不留神他们就会溜进来\N{\rEng}There are a lot of little thieves out there. One of them could get into your house.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.29,1:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是你没关门的话\N{\rEng}Especially if you leave the door open.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.82,1:09:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也能在这里祈祷\N{\rEng}You can pray here too.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.87,1:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里或是大会堂,对上帝而言是殊途同归\N{\rEng}Here or in the synagogue, to God it's the same difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.34,1:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,过来坐下\N{\rEng}Come over here and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.61,1:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"我的良人,白而且红(《雅歌》)\N{\rEng}"My beloved is white and ruddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.66,1:09:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"他的皮肤像至纯的金\N{\rEng}His skin is as the most fine gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.46,1:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"他的两腮如香花畦"\N{\rEng}His cheeks are as a bed of spices."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.26,1:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他自从去年十二月就没梳洗过\N{\rEng}Even though he hasn't washed since last December.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.36,1:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"他的眼如鸽子眼\N{\rEng}"His eyes are as the eyes of doves.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.50,1:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"他的身体如象牙\N{\rEng}His body is as bright ivory.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.38,1:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"他的双腿如同白玉石柱"\N{\rEng}His legs are as pillars of marble."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.18,1:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在肮脏的裤管里孤立着\N{\rEng}In pants so dirty they stand by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.86,1:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"他全然可爱"\N{\rEng}"He is altogether lovable."
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.62,1:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但他永远都会是个小瘪三\N{\rEng}But he'll always be a two-bit punk...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.37,1:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他永远不会成为我的爱人,真可惜\N{\rEng}...so he'll never be my beloved. What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.65,1:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有人\N{\rEng}Somebody's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.01,1:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人啊\N{\rEng}There ain't nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.41,1:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是麦克希\N{\rEng}It's Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.84,1:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,原来就是他\N{\rEng}Ah, so that's who it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.68,1:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.65,1:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快去吧,你妈在叫你了\N{\rEng}Go on, run. Your mother's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.46,1:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,面条\N{\rEng}Noodles!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.01,1:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看他要怎样\N{\rEng}Just gonna go see what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.74,1:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨　- 嘿\N{\rEng}- Hey. - Yo?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.42,1:12:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在这待了很久?　- 没有\N{\rEng}- You been here long? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.76,1:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是你在里面?\N{\rEng}Were you in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.39,1:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的吻功真是差劲\N{\rEng}You're one lousy kisser.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.77,1:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我办完事后看见你走进去\N{\rEng}I seen you go in there after that ball-buster.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.11,1:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是昨晚的成果,银器四块钱,打字机六块\N{\rEng}Here's the stuff from last night. We got 4 for the silverware, 6 for the typewriter.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.26,1:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的利普希茨只肯出这个价,我们该另寻买主了\N{\rEng}Shitty Lipschitz wouldn't cough up any more. We gotta get somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.77,1:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来和你分钱的!\N{\rEng}I came to divvy up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.90,1:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明天和大伙一起分吧　- 我也是来接你的\N{\rEng}- Tomorrow, with the others. - I also came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.00,1:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我现在没空　- 那些房子和商店都空无一人\N{\rEng}- I can't come right now. -The houses, the stores are all empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.21,1:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以大干一场,你却要去泡妞\N{\rEng}We got our pick. You pick that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.30,1:13:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.28,1:13:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么有你这样的搭档,玩你的去吧\N{\rEng}Some partner I got. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.64,1:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,生意如何?小子们\N{\rEng}How's it going, boys?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.93,1:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\rEng}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.52,1:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,霸哥\N{\rEng}Bugsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.77,1:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你们自立门户了?\N{\rEng}I hear you guys are in business for yourselves now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.36,1:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且混得不错\N{\rEng}I hear youse are doing real good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.50,1:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不把我介绍给你朋友?\N{\rEng}Ain't you gonna introduce me to your friend here?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.22,1:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是自我介绍一下吧\N{\rEng}I'll introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.70,1:14:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了\N{\rEng}Excuse the glove.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.39,1:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\rEng}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.44,1:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这一份是我的\N{\rEng}That's my cut.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.74,1:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿,你们只能为我工作\N{\rEng}You don't work for me, you don't work for no one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.75,1:15:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢替别人工作\N{\rEng}I don't like bosses.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.04,1:15:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是滚回布朗克斯比较好\N{\rEng}You was better off you stayed in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.76,1:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你的日子也一样会好过些\N{\rEng}It would have been better for you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.85,1:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早晚我会杀了他　- 是吗?\N{\rEng}- I'm gonna kill him one of these days. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.43,1:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可现在我们已经被他打个半死了\N{\rEng}Meantime it looks like he's killed us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.23,1:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,黛博拉,快开门\N{\rEng}Deborah, open up the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.23,1:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,黛博拉,快开门\N{\rEng}Deborah, open up the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.74,1:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,黛博拉\N{\rEng}Deborah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.34,1:17:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 俱乐部的东西准备好了吗　- 我们正在装车\N{\rEng}- That stuff, is it ready for the club? - We're loading it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.75,1:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这他妈的是怎么回事?　- 阿尔,今天有"大人物"大驾光临\N{\rEng}- Hey, che cazzo succede down here? - AI, we got the big boys with us today.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.68,1:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们要替我们工作　- 做霸哥的工作,我们要取代他\N{\rEng}- They wanna work for us. -Doing what Bugsy did. We want his job.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.56,1:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听见了吗?\N{\rEng}Do you get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.90,1:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将是你最好的护航人员\N{\rEng}Hey, Capuano, we the best escorts you ever gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.08,1:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,护你个头,赶紧给我滚吧\N{\rEng}A fangulo a ma, escort your mother's ass out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.38,1:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好,我们走吧,面条,去别的地方兜售你的新发明\N{\rEng}Okay. Let's go, Noodles. We'll peddle your invention somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.39,1:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,留步\N{\rEng}Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.32,1:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么发明?\N{\rEng}What invention?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.53,1:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们的货是走水路,对吧?　- 有时候是\N{\rEng}- You ship your stuff by the river, right? -Si, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.62,1:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当你们被海防队抓到,就得把所有货都扔海里\N{\rEng}And when you get caught by the coast guard, you gotta throw all the cases overboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.37,1:19:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你把整船货都丢了　- 所以呢?\N{\rEng}- You lose the whole shipment, Capuano. - So?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.25,1:19:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们抽一成,我们就保证你的货全部安然上岸\N{\rEng}For 10 percent, we'll save it all for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.13,1:19:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们难不成有潜水艇吗?　- 我们有盐\N{\rEng}- What do you got, a submarine? - We got salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.39,1:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有什么?\N{\rEng}You got what?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.11,1:19:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 盐,我们需要盐　- 对,每批货需要三吨的盐\N{\rEng}- Salts, me and the boys are rolling salts. - Yeah. We need 3 tons of salt per shipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.12,1:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧滚吧,滚回学校念书去\N{\rEng}Get the fuck out of here. Go back to school where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.12,1:19:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要这么多盐有什么用?\N{\rEng}What is it with all this salt?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.80,1:19:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,面条有带盐来,让他们见识一下吧\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, we got salt on our Noodles. Show 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.00,1:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面都是盐\N{\rEng}This is full of salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.97,1:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,过来\N{\rEng}All right, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.71,1:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后呢?　- 别着急啊\N{\rEng}- So? - Keep your shirt on, Capuano.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.55,1:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得等盐溶解\N{\rEng}We gotta wait for the salt to dissolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.41,1:20:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如何?　- 出问题了吗?\N{\rEng}- Well? - Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.52,1:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rEng}Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.77,1:20:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒\N{\rEng}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.11,1:21:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.83,1:21:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你瞧瞧　- 太棒了\N{\rEng}- Look at that! - It's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.50,1:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条　- 看啊\N{\rEng}- Noodles. - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.55,1:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我看见了,我说什么来着?　- 对\N{\rEng}- I see 'em! What did I tell you? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.56,1:21:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.54,1:21:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条　- 万岁!万岁!\N{\rEng}- Hey, Noodles. - Hooray. Hooray for us!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.10,1:21:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了\N{\rEng}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.56,1:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,过来,麦克希\N{\rEng}Come here, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.53,1:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们成功了　- 不要,麦克希…\N{\rEng}- We did it. - No, Max, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.58,1:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.50,1:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.61,1:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Max!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.54,1:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Max!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.19,1:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少了我你该怎么办?\N{\rEng}What would you do without me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.10,1:23:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\rEng}There.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.69,1:23:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起,我们我们设立我们的联合基金\N{\rEng}From here on, we establish the shared funds of the gang.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.16,1:23:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,钱属于我们共同所有,不属于任何个人\N{\rEng}They belong to all of us together and to none of us alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.33,1:23:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议我们存下每一笔收入的一半,同意吗?\N{\rEng}And we solemnly swear to put in 50 percent of everything we make. Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.84,1:23:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\rEng}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.39,1:23:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 同意　- 同意\N{\rEng}- Agreed. - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.35,1:23:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\rEng}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.11,1:24:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要再看一眼\N{\rEng}I wanna take another peek.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.54,1:24:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这交给肥摩,但我们不告诉他钥匙的用途\N{\rEng}This goes to Fat Moe. We don't tell him what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.38,1:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只有当我们在场时,他才能交还给我们钥匙\N{\rEng}And he gives it back only when we're all together.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.89,1:24:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,同意吗?\N{\rEng}Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.23,1:24:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\rEng}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.36,1:24:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\rEng}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.40,1:25:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,霸哥来了,快跑\N{\rEng}Bugsy's coming! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.13,1:26:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,面条…\N{\rEng}Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.01,1:26:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我滑倒了\N{\rEng}I slipped.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.25,1:28:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\rEng}Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.74,1:28:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,混帐东西\N{\rEng}Schmuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.52,1:30:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}(你们之中哪怕是最年轻最强壮的,也都会倒在上帝的剑下)
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.91,1:30:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要进去吗?\N{\rEng}Wanna go in?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.43,1:30:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.26,1:30:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是亲属吗?\N{\rEng}You a relative?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.52,1:31:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叔叔\N{\rEng}An uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.34,1:31:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,打开了\N{\rEng}It's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.72,1:34:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,(情同手足的朋友,为纪念永恒的回忆而立)\N{\rEng}"Erected to their everlasting memory by their friend and brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.31,1:34:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,(大卫艾伦森,一九六七年)\N{\rEng}...David Aaronson, 1967."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.83,1:35:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,有什么需要的吗\N{\rEng}Hello. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.37,1:35:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只是随便看看　- 我是这里的主管\N{\rEng}- I was just looking around. - I'm the director of Riverdale.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.34,1:35:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未见过如此的陵墓\N{\rEng}I've never seen a tomb like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.05,1:35:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称之为天堂,这样的说法显得更平和些\N{\rEng}We like to call them "heavens", we find it's more comforting.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.89,1:35:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,情同手足的朋友,为纪念永恒的回忆而立\N{\rEng}Erected to their everlasting memory by their friend and brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.64,1:35:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大卫艾伦森,一九六七年\N{\rEng}David Aaronson, 1967.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.60,1:35:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是新建的吗?\N{\rEng}Is it a new building?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.65,1:35:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的,您认识艾伦森先生吗?抱歉,您怎么称呼?\N{\rEng}Yes. Do you know Mr. Aaronson, Mr...? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.95,1:35:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉斯\N{\rEng}Mr. Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.57,1:35:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉斯先生,您能有兴趣是我们建筑师的荣幸\N{\rEng}Mr. Williams. An interest like yours is a compliment to our architects, Mr. Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.83,1:35:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,您先请\N{\rEng}After you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.36,1:36:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得其内在与外在一样美\N{\rEng}I think the beauty of the interior equals that of the exterior.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.07,1:36:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,您同意吗?威廉斯先生\N{\rEng}Don't you agree, Mr. Williams?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.37,1:36:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想把它做成三十年代的风格\N{\rEng}We wanted to do the style of the 30s,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.16,1:36:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你年轻时的朋友们去世时的年代\N{\rEng}which is when our young friends went away.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.13,1:36:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是艾伦森的主意吗?\N{\rEng}Was it Mr. Aaronson's idea?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.14,1:36:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上他全交给我们了\N{\rEng}Actually he left the whole thing up to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.72,1:36:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得到了全权委托\N{\rEng}We had carte blanche.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.19,1:36:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他唯一的建议就是那段铭文\N{\rEng}All he suggested was the inscription.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.65,1:36:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"情同手足的朋友,为纪念永恒的回忆而立"\N{\rEng}"Your youngest and strongest will fall by the sword."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.36,1:36:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那音乐呢?　- 音乐\N{\rEng}- What about the music? - And the music.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.36,1:37:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也是他的主意吗?　- 是的\N{\rEng}- That was exactly his suggestion? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.37,1:37:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们收到了一盘磁带\N{\rEng}We received a tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.66,1:37:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很了解他\N{\rEng}You seem to know him so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.29,1:37:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能告诉他你又多喜欢这座"天堂"\N{\rEng}I'd like to ask you to tell him how much you like the "heaven",
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.21,1:37:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当你遇见他的时候,可以吗?　- 没问题\N{\rEng}- when you see him. Could you do that? -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.22,1:37:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经离开这里好多年,我已经没有他的地址了\N{\rEng}I've been away quite a long time and I lost the address.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.30,1:37:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你能…\N{\rEng}Maybe you...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.39,1:37:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要票据或者别的什么吧\N{\rEng}You must have signed a bill or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.98,1:37:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在银行那里,一个外国银行\N{\rEng}The bank handled it. A foreign bank.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.02,1:37:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望我能帮到你,威廉斯先生\N{\rEng}I wish I could be of more assistance to you, Mr. Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.36,1:37:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你想过建造你自己的天堂吗?\N{\rEng}Have you ever thought to build your own heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.94,1:38:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑一下\N{\rEng}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.93,1:39:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(下次工作的订金)
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.89,1:40:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你拿吧,先生\N{\rEng}Can I take that for you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.56,1:40:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,您的礼车在等你\N{\rEng}Your limousine is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.03,1:41:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克希\N{\rEng}Maxie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.33,1:41:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别来无恙,叔叔?你看上去气色不错\N{\rEng}How are you, uncle? You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.75,1:41:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去更好\N{\rEng}You're looking a little better.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.09,1:41:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧,我载你离开\N{\rEng}Come on. Better get you off the streets.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.27,1:41:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 豪华礼车　- 这还用说?\N{\rEng}- Some limousine. - What are you talking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.90,1:41:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在开公司了,那是个很好的幌子,能赚很多钱\N{\rEng}We own the company now. It's a good cover. It pays off too.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.61,1:41:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈写信给我说你在赚死人的钱\N{\rEng}My mother wrote me you was in the body-snatching business.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.82,1:41:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你为我家人做的一切\N{\rEng}By the way, I appreciate everything you did for my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.28,1:41:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你太见外了,那是你的钱\N{\rEng}Forget it. It's your dough.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.16,1:41:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都白纸黑字写在公司的账本里\N{\rEng}It's all down in black and white in the company books.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.33,1:42:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是合伙人,你,派希还有斜眼\N{\rEng}You're the company. You and Patsy and Cockeye.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.25,1:42:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都是挖墓工兼合伙人\N{\rEng}Gravediggers and equal partners.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.96,1:42:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不说这个了,我们先办正事吧\N{\rEng}Hey, enough of this. Business before pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.93,1:42:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有个要事要办\N{\rEng}We got a rush job. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.89,1:42:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,过来,看看这个,过来\N{\rEng}Come here. Look at this. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.56,1:42:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,猝死,真他妈的可惜,对吧?\N{\rEng}Sudden death. Fucking tragedy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.61,1:42:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 二十六岁　- 二十六?\N{\rEng}- 26 years old. - 26?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.61,1:42:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真可惜　- 全身僵硬,死于嗑药过度\N{\rEng}- What a shame. -Great stiff. She died of an overdose.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.12,1:42:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算再爽一次\N{\rEng}And I'm ready for another.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.29,1:42:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为他诸如生命吧,你在牢里没变成同性恋吧?\N{\rEng}Pump the life into her. You didn't turn pansy in there, did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.50,1:42:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受吧\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.92,1:42:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在墓园里翻云覆雨,他们经常如此\N{\rEng}Turning over in the grave. They do it every time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.30,1:43:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心,他不是同性恋\N{\rEng}Don't worry. A pansy he ain't.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.81,1:43:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你　- 不客气,面条\N{\rEng}- Thanks. - You're welcome, Noodles.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.93,1:43:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rEng}Whoops. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.06,1:43:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了,晚安\N{\rEng}Thanks. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.94,1:43:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,想去喝一杯吗?\N{\rEng}Hey, you want a little pick-me-up?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.61,1:43:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不了,谢谢,我已经爽过了\N{\rEng}No, thanks. I've had mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.61,1:43:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是全力以赴了吗?　- 你以为呢?\N{\rEng}- Did you give her your all? - What do you think? You bet your life in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.39,1:44:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,带你去瞧瞧那地方\N{\rEng}Wait till you see this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.44,1:44:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿\N{\rEng}It's over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.19,1:44:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们这是去哪儿　- 一个永不打烊的地方\N{\rEng}- Where we going? - To a place that never closes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.74,1:44:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,小心\N{\rEng}Whoops. Watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.21,1:44:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哪里?\N{\rEng}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.42,1:44:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地盘,城里最棒的地方\N{\rEng}Our place. We got the hottest spot in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.98,1:45:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是正宗的肥摩俱乐部\N{\rEng}This is the real Fat Moe's.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.94,1:45:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子给他\N{\rEng}Get rid of that rag, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.19,1:45:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得如何　- 很漂亮\N{\rEng}- What do you think? - It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.78,1:45:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢吗　- 真是漂亮\N{\rEng}- You like it? - Beautiful. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.55,1:45:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,给我\N{\rEng}Hey, give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.59,1:45:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条　- 派希,看看谁来了\N{\rEng}- Noodles. - Patsy, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.97,1:45:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,过来,臭小子,快过来!\N{\rEng}Come here, son of a bitch. Come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.94,1:45:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你看上去棒极了　- 稍等\N{\rEng}- You look fantastic. - Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.40,1:45:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,近况如何\N{\rEng}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.65,1:45:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你壮了好多　- 我?\N{\rEng}- Look how big you got. - Me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.03,1:45:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,面条,天啊\N{\rEng}Noodles. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.91,1:46:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 面条　- 三号来了\N{\rEng}- Noodles! - Number three coming through.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.91,1:46:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们来一起干一杯\N{\rEng}Let's have a toast, for chrissakes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.83,1:46:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你样子糟透了　- 刚从监狱出来嘛\N{\rEng}- You look like shit. - What do you want? I just got out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.63,1:46:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好家伙　- 嘿,面条,来一杯吧\N{\rEng}- Nice guy. - Hey, Noodles, get a load of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.26,1:46:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEng}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.97,1:46:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,苏格兰威士忌\N{\rEng}Hey, scotch heating.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.09,1:46:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一杯一块钱\N{\rEng}Yeah, a buck a cup.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.22,1:46:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一杯一块钱　- 是啊\N{\rEng}- A buck a cup? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.85,1:46:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 成本呢?　- 成本?\N{\rEng}- How much it cost us? - Costing us?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.77,1:46:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对　- 总成本才一毛钱\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - A dime, including overhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.81,1:46:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿,面条　- 肥摩\N{\rEng}- Hey, Noodles. - Fat Moe.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.16,1:46:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去好极了\N{\rEng}You look terrific.
